reviewText:
I found it very disappointing, the sound made it impossible to watch.
I understand it was filmed at a lecture,but not very professional.

It's pretty trippy to me that ufo sightings and encounters have happened around the world. Same thing with bigfoot sightings, etc.  This dvd is exploring a case from England but the details are quite similar to those you hear about from other parts of the world. Seems like more than a coincidence to me. Behind the similarities lies the truth.  This is just a piece of the puzzle.
I've been a ufo buff for some time but had never heard of this particular incident. Quite a fascinating story that details possible British and US government involvement in the subsequent cover up.

Top quality all around, in all areas.  No problems. Mailed on time, well packed, lived up to my high expectations.
It blows my mind how much is hidden from us and how we are basically treated like children by the government. The info presented here is just the tip of the iceberg I'm sure.

The Rendlesham Forest Incidents are some of the most interesting of their kind.  There are many eyewitnesses, & is amazing that they were able to cover up such events.  This does a great job of covering in detail what actually happened.
It's a few poorly recorded speeches. It looks and sounds like it was made with a handheld camera. Unwatchable garbage.
What a great item.  I have waited a long time to get this.  I will watch it again and again.
